Two programs are included: 
Fifoserver is a daemon program, which means that you can close terminal after launching it
and it'll continue working in background. 
Fifoclient allows you to transfer data to fifoserver which then copies files into new files. 



Installation

Build both programs:
make

cleans both output files:	
make clean

deletes all files of both programs (!) :		
make uninstall	



Usage

Launch daemon:
./fifoserver

Find daemon's pid:
find fileserver

Kill daemon:
kill (pid)

To transfer files:
./fifoclient FILENAME1 





